   <summary>This module provides functionality to run unit and functional tests for Magento using phpUnit.</summary>
   <description>This module provides a patched version of Mage_Core enabling you to inject testing dependencies at run time. Due to the functionality of the Varien_Autoloader the local code pool is prioritised over the core. Meaning that any code duplicated from the Mage vendor namespace into the local code pool will be used over the core.

This allows you to build and run functional controller tests in the same way you would with a standard Zend Framework Application using [Zend Test](http://framework.zend.com/manual/en/zend.test.phpunit.html). This mocks the Request and Response objects to that you can query the Response within a suite of tests.</description>
